headline: Akamai Inference Cloud Transforms AI from Core to Edge with NVIDIA
summary: Akamai Technologies, Inc. (NASDAQ:AKAM) today launched Akamai Inference Cloud, a platform that redefines where and how AI is used by expanding inference from core data centers to the edge of the internet.
